---
title: Duck Breast and Fig Sauce with Creamy Garlic Mash
description: Fig jam adds an elegant sweetness to balance out the richness of crisp, golden duck skin. Simple in steps, but oh-so-luxurious, this supper will make you feel like you're in a restaurant on date night!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/duck-breast-and-fig-sauce-3b7cedb3.jpg
